# CodeSage (Starter) — Ingestion + Parsing + Embeddings (API Only)

This repo is a working starting point for CodeSage implementing:
- Repository ingestion (clone/pull)
- Parsing (Python AST → functions/classes/modules)
- Code representation & embedding layer (function-level)
- FastAPI endpoints to ingest, browse, embed, delete

## Quickstart
```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # Windows PS: .\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -U pip
pip install -e .
uvicorn codesage.api.main:app --reload
```
Swagger: http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

### Enable transformer embeddings (optional)
```bash
pip install -e ".[embeddings]"
```

## Embedding endpoints
- POST /embed/repos/{repo_id}
- GET /repos/{repo_id}/embeddings
- GET /units/{unit_id}/embedding
